Product name: Personalised Duo Destination Wedding Guest Book - Map Guest Book - Wooden Guest Book - Travel Wedding - Destination Map - Couples Gift
Description:
A personalised destination map guest book, beautifully engraved with your choice of two locations and bespoke wording to make your guest book completely unique to you!
This guest book can be personalised with any two destinations of your choice, be it home countries, places you have visited, or significant destinations of any kind.
Simply choose your two favoured destinations, and off you go!
The book comprises of 30 sheets (60 sides) of high quality 160gsm ivory paper as standard, with two sheets of 175gsm embossed paper at the front and back, in a bespoke engraved birch wooden cover. The two sheets of coloured paper will determine the colour of the heart, as seen through the cut out section of the front cover. Take a look at our colour swatch image to choose the shade that suits you.
Additional guest book paper can be purchased from the link below:
https://www.etsy.com/listing/160498911/10-extra-guest-book-sheets
Accentuate your guest book by adding a bespoke mini heart token, engraved for extra detail with your specific wording upto a maximum of 25 characters, including spaces. To include a mini heart with your order, make sure to select an option which includes a mini heart token from the drop down menu when choosing the size of your guest book!
Our Twig Pens are available to add to your order via the link below, to ensure that your guests 'sign in' in style! Why not include an engraved Twig Pen, to make it even more personal to you!
https://www.etsy.com/uk/listing/191093118/twig-pen
At Clouds and Currents, we love to get things right, first time. We'll email you a digital proof of your design, usually within 2-3 days of accepting your order, so you can check the details before we go ahead and create your bespoke guest book.
Please note that delays in approving the proof may lengthen the dispatch date.
Each of our guest books are created solely in the UK, using only the highest quality papers and birch wood. An A5 guest book measures 212mm x 150mm, and an A4 guest book measures 303mm x 215mm
This Clouds and Currents product is crafted and finished by hand in our studio in rural Essex and each item is made to order. 
______________ How to Order _____________
Choose the size of guest book (with or without mini heart token) you require from the drop down menu. From the second drop down menu, choose the colour of paper you would like for the front and back inner sheets, and then and add the item to your cart. In the 'Notes to Clouds and Currents' box please include the following information:
1. First line wording (30 characters maximum) (if required)
2. Second line wording (30 characters maximum) (if required)
3. Third line wording (30 characters maximum) (if required)
4. Country 1 (15 characters maximum) (required)
5. Description of country 1 (e.g. the proposal) (15 characters maximum)
6. Location of heart cut-out 1 (25 characters maximum)
7. Country 2 (15 characters maximum) (required)
8. Description of country 2 (e.g. the wedding) (15 characters maximum)
9. Location of heart cut-out 2 (25 characters maximum)
10. Mini heart personalisation (only required if the mini heart token option is chosen above) (25 characters maximum)
